data.description: This delightful Cielo Vista home is conveniently situated 2 minutes from I-10!  Recent updates include the installation of windows and front landscaping. This single-level beauty features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and comes complete with refrigerated air. You'll find a designated dining area and a separate living room for your comfort. The spacious den, complete with a fireplace, is perfect for hosting festive holiday gatherings. Need an office or playroom? A versatile flex space is available to suit your needs. Centrally located, this home provides easy access to all parts of El Paso and Ft. Bliss.  Like to travel or have frequent visitors?  It's just minutes away from the airport. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity!
